metadata.title: Archeology Preliminary Sites - EVOS

creators.name: USDA Forest Service, Alaska Department of Natural Resources

metadata.description: Data Type: Cultural Resources; This data contains pre-edited archeological site data, that is an extraction of data from the Alaska Heritage Resource Survey. Data was provided by Dept. of Natural Resources, Office of History for the spill affected area of the Exxon Valdez oil spill. This data was released to provide information for spill response, and damage assessment only. These data are closed to the general public as required by PL 96-95;AS 9.25.120 exception 4; Policy and Procedure No. 50200.
